> doesn't help.  I had a local mechanic (VW spec.) look at it, and he felt
> that both the clutch and the trans were in good shape.  The only clue he
> offered was that the clutch lever is longer than stock.  I have replaced
> the clutch cable and adjusted properly.  Clutch does not slip.  Trans
> does not pop out of any gears.  Anyone have any ideas?
